ded anthropological fable, a story about the state of nature that is intended to illustrate its principles.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aPolitical psychology. 0aSmall groups. 0aSocial psychology. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015768040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300157680423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300157680/original  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles